name: Caedrel's ZaZa Tree
description:
This tree is the result of the fight of ex-league pro and twitch streamer Caedrel and the spanish streamer pedrodbr.

The canvas displays the image of the 7tv emote ZAZA which is frequently used in Caedrel's stream chat.
The words "The Fraud" which can be seen in the bottom left corner at the end of the canvas are dedicated to the chinese LPL player TheShy, who has a history of inting whilst being praised one of the best players to ever exist by Caedrel.
